billycock
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:an old word for a bowler hat, any of various low round-crowned hats worn by men (occas. used of a `bowler' hat (contrast ? hard-hitter'); -also billycock hat


Origin: [none]
